parameters.name: T_e
parameters.description: electron temperature in the GDZ-sph coordinate system, dependent on time, lon, lat, height

parameters.name: v_nup_ilev
parameters.description: vertical neutral wind velocity (up) in the GDZ-sph coordinate system, dependent on time, lon, lat, ilev

parameters.name: T_n
parameters.description: neutral temperature in the GDZ-sph coordinate system, dependent on time, lon, lat, height

parameters.name: TEC
parameters.description: vertical total electron content (height integrated from bottom to top boundary) in the GDZ-sph coordinate system, dependent on time, lon, lat

parameters.name: E_theta300km
parameters.description: Electric field at 300 km, theta component in the GDZ-sph coordinate system, dependent on time, Elon, Elat
